QuestData.Title: The Rise of Aku'mai
QuestData.Description: We barely escaped the Twilight's Hammer sacrificial altar, but there are others who need help deeper within these caves. If these cultists complete their blood ritual, they will unleash Aku'mai the Devourer onto the world. You cannot let this happen.
QuestData.RewardText: That was incredible, $n! The Old Gods will think twice before trying to crawl out of their pit again.
